title: Mixtape Game - Please Welcome, Zach Dillon!
description:
Mixtape Game hosted by Drake this week w/ Special Guest  Zach Dillon! //

You're sitting at a Roulette Table at a casino. You're down $5000 and have only $1000 left. You decide to put everything on the number one and... IT HITS! You just won $35,000! What song plays as this happens? // 

You got recruited by the Minnesota Twins. It's your first time appearing on the field, and you'll be up to bat soon. What's the song you listen to to hype yourself up as you sit nervously in the dugout? // 

We have KDWB's Lake Patrol going on the rest of summer. Give me your 'It's Summer On The Lake' theme song that you're playing!
